## Description {#details}

A class that contains all <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/unwindrow">UnwindRow</a> objects for an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/fde">FDE</a> or a single unwind row for a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cie">CIE</a>.

To unwind an address the rows, which are sorted by start address, can be searched to find the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/unwindrow">UnwindRow</a> with the lowest starting address that is greater than or equal to the address that is being looked up.

Definition at line 321 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugframe-h">DWARFDebugFrame.h</a>.

## Private Member Functions

### parseRows() {#ac27a9e392fa6593b1149cd43e9dd59ed}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>Error UnwindTable::parseRows (<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cfiprogram">CFIProgram</a> &amp; CFIP, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/unwindrow">UnwindRow</a> &amp; CurrRow, <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/registerlocations">RegisterLocations</a> &#42; InitialLocs)</>}>
Parse the information in the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cfiprogram">CFIProgram</a> and update the CurrRow object that the state machine describes.

This is an internal implementation that emulates the state machine described in the DWARF Call Frame Information opcodes and will push CurrRow onto the Rows container when needed.


<ParametersList title="Parameters">
<ParametersListItem name="CFIP">the CFI program that contains the opcodes from a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cie">CIE</a> or <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/fde">FDE</a>.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="CurrRow">the current row to modify while parsing the state machine.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="InitialLocs">If non-NULL, we are parsing a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/fde">FDE</a> and this contains the initial register locations from the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cie">CIE</a>. If NULL, then a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cie">CIE</a>&#39;s opcodes are being parsed and this is not needed. This is used for the DW&#95;CFA&#95;restore and DW&#95;CFA&#95;restore&#95;extended opcodes.</ParametersListItem>
</ParametersList>

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugframe-h/#l00395">395</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugframe-h">DWARFDebugFrame.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/debuginfo/lib/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugframe-cpp/#l00515">515</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/debuginfo/lib/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugframe-cpp">DWARFDebugFrame.cpp</a>.
</MemberDefinition>
